{"tid":1389440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(請即行動) 大家一齊成為陪審員啦!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-31T02:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T09:04:02.000Z","uid":122174,"like":98,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"28280417607d66b65194df60ce09fad729d890e9","tid":1389440,"uid":122174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"今朝打左電話去問！有手足要補充請隨便！<br />\n<br />\n如果想申請返做陪審員，需要交以下文件並寄回。<br />\n<br />\n1)寫一封信表明出任陪審員是香港人對社會的責任,希望自的名字能被列入陪審員名單。<br />\n要有自己全名,ID no.,出生日期,及簽署<br />\n(如果有手足有時間請整個template 俾大家填，感謝！)<br />\n<br />\n2)填好ROP-18 form:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fpdforms%2Frop18.pdf&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij8dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=3e24daaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/pdforms/rop18.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n3)學歷證明文件副本<br />\n<br />\n寄去:<br />\n香港灣仔告士打道7號<br />\n入境事務大樓12樓<br />\n人事登記陪審員登記小組<br />\n<br />\n人事入境事務處: 2829 3356<br />\n&mdash;&gt;查詢想申請返嘅相關事宜<br />\n<br />\n高等法院電話:2825 4668<br />\n&mdash;&gt;check下自己是否on陪審員list <br />\n<br />\n同人事果個先生問過，都需時一個月先會處理到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xuu4ruO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuu4ruO.png&h=07c56bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快啲做野！盡返公民嘅責任啦！叫埋你身邊嘅朋友一齊交！</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"8ddd72792bbe51dd76dbc89cad83be0f342b773d","tid":1389440,"uid":122174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:14:46.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!"},{"pid":"40c6570dcc7b35b365181a0fbb135e07c865554a","tid":1389440,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a7be268dad8902dc78680e7f2a402bd6bcaa76d","tid":1389440,"uid":213781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"推"}